latestPosts.caption:
⭐️ NOW REPRESENTING ⭐️ #Makeup Artist @alanapalaumakeup ✨✨

Alana is gifted in her technical, artistic and natural approach to #beauty. Her exceptional roster of beauty brands and commercial clients includes @saiebeauty @rarebeauty @maccosmetics @google @burberry @warbyparker @nike @boss and @diesel.

Further, her collaborations with visionary photographers such as Collier Schorr, Micaiah Carter and Petra Collins has featured her work in @i_d, @harpersbazaarus, @glamourmag, @nytstyle and more. 

Alana’s #celebrity clientele lists icons such as Ms. Lauryn Hill, Frank Ocean, Anderson .Paak, Kaytranada and Coco Jones. 

Alana is bicoastal in #LA & #NY. ✨

latestPosts.caption:
My daddy gained his wings today after a long fought cancer battle. Words can’t describe the overwhelming aching that I’m feeling. I feel blessed that I got the chance to thank him for the unconditional love, for passing down his wit and sense of humor, for all of the guttural laughs, freestyles and joy. This caption will never fully illustrate just how great of a man he truly was. The words are escaping me - the grief is too strong right now. Thank you Jesus for blessing me with such a wonderful father. I wish we had a bit more time together. He’s with our people now. I will continue to love him until the end of time. Forever and always, 
my daddini. ❤️♦️🕊️
